verbose_text: The benefits of autologous PRP can be summarized as follows : (1) offers high potency : multiple growth factors are present in high concentrations within PRP; (2) has the ability to produce the desired effect : PRP prevented excessive collagen deposition and controlled well organized collagen deposit; and (3) consists of both quantitative and qualitative components : PRP appeared to help maintain the layered structure of the injured vocal fold.
